Gaël Coupée            — French (proofreading)
Detlef Kahner          — German
Luc Pauwels            — Dutch
Fabio Concas           — Italian (original)
Gianluca Abbiati       — Italian (updated for v2.8.2)
Chir                   — Spanish
Mauricio               — Brazilian Portuguese
